[Diabetes mellitus: Contribution to changes in the life expectancy in Mexico 
1990, 2000, and 2010].

[Article in Spanish]

Dávila-Cervantes CA(1), Pardo Montaño AM(2).

Author information:
(1)Facultad Latinoamericana de Ciencias Sociales (FLACSO), México, DF, México, 
claudio.davila@flacso.edu.mx.
(2)Universidad Nacional Autónoma de México (UNAM), México, DF, México, 
