Forensic ancestry analysis with two capillary electrophoresis ancestry 
informative marker (AIM) panels: Results of a collaborative EDNAP exercise.

Santos C(1), Fondevila M(1), Ballard D(2), Banemann R(3), Bento AM(4), Børsting 
C(5), Branicki W(6), Brisighelli F(7), Burrington M(8), Capal T(9), Chaitanya 
